snippet.title: ROM Check Fail Gameplay
snippet.description:
ROM Check Fail is an action game by Farbs where players have to eliminate all enemies to complete each level. The task is made a little more difficult by the random switching of gameplay rules where ideas are recycled and remastered as an odd mix of arcade or console classics from the past. This game is fun to play, but it can sometimes be hard to get rid of the enemies. But overall, this game can be amazing to try out.

Since the link doesn't work anymore, I don't know where else to get the game.
